# Axonary — SEO rules

**Domain:** https://axonary.com  
**Maintainer:** Update the registry and sections when routes or primaries change.  
**QA before publish:** See `governance.mdc` (mandatory checklist).

---

## A. SEO intent architecture

- **TOFU:** Awareness / education — problems and concepts; low product specificity.  
- **MOFU:** Consideration — compares approaches and providers; solution-aware.  
- **BOFU:** Decision — ready to engage, hire, or buy; high commercial intent.

**Rule:** One URL = one intent (strict). Do not mix TOFU education with BOFU hire/sale CTAs on the same URL without splitting.

**Blog (`/blog/:slug`):** Set intent per post in the brief. Default new posts to **TOFU** unless tied to a BOFU offer.

---

## B. Keyword ownership

- One **primary** keyword per URL — H1, title, first ~100 words.  
- **No cannibalization** — one owner per primary; use canonical, 301, merge, or differentiate secondaries only in body.  
- Secondary keywords: unlimited in body/H2s/anchors; never replace primary in H1/title.

---

## C. On-page structure

- **H1:** Exact-match **primary keyword** (registry below). No brand-only H1 on indexable money pages.  
- **H2 topics (required):** Problem, Solution, Features, Benefits, Use Cases, CTA — headings may vary if intent is obvious.  
- **Length:** Service-style pages **800–1200** words; blogs **1200–1800** (main copy only). Legal/utility: as needed.  
- **Deliverable:** State word count in PR/changelog for service and blog content.

---

## D. NLP / semantic layer

- **15–25** named entities per page; list in a **Semantic entities** block in draft or PR. Minimum **15+** for gate.  
- CRM/sales pages: include CRM semantics (pipeline, lead, opportunity, account, workflow automation, integrations, etc.) where accurate.

---

## E. Internal linking

- **Home** → every major service cluster within **two clicks**.  
- **Service pages** ↔ related services + parent hub (`/services`, etc.).  
- **Blogs** → services (conversion anchors); **blogs** ↔ blogs (clusters).  
- **Anchors (sitewide target):** ~20% exact / ~50% partial / ~30% branded.

---

## F. Meta

- **Title:** 55–60 characters; primary keyword + intent signal.  
- **Description:** 140–155 characters; benefit + CTA.

---

## G. Schema (JSON-LD)

| Page type | Type |
|-----------|------|
| Homepage | `Organization` (+ `WebSite` if used; fix broken `SearchAction` when implementing) |
| Service / hire / industry / tech | `Service` (per Google guidelines) |
| Blog posts | `Article` |
| FAQ blocks | `FAQPage` |

Keep `@id` and `url` aligned with canonical URLs.

